To everyone that just started working out and stumble upon this video, DO NOT give up. I know at first it seems hard, I stop myself halfway through (my body screaming at me not to continue 😂 always try to push yourself but listen to your body at the same time). I do this twice a day, alternating with other workouts vid and a week later I can do this full video in one time (not at emi’s pace yet but I’m aiming for it 🔥). Go at your own pace, what important is DON’T give up. We can do this! 💪🏻🔥
